1. *Nikad* nisam bila tamo. (I have never been there.)
2. *Ikad* nisam završila zadatak u roku. (I have never finished the task on time.)
3. Možda ću *ikad* imati priliku da vidim to. (Maybe I will ever have a chance to see it.)
4. Svi mi kažu da *nikad* neću biti uspešan. (Everyone tells me I will never be successful.)
5. *Nikad* se ne zna šta će se desiti. (You never know what will happen.)